  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-hypervisor support (KVM, VMware vSphere, XenServer, XCP-ng, Hyper-V)",
    "Compute orchestration with VM lifecycle management",
    "Network-as-a-Service with VPC, VPN, firewall, and load balancing",
    "Primary and secondary storage management",
    "Multi-tenancy with accounts, domains, and role-based access control",
    "Kubernetes cluster management via CKS (CloudStack Kubernetes Service)",
    "Comprehensive REST API with query-based interface",
    "High availability and disaster recovery support",
    "Extensive plugin system for hypervisors, networking, and storage",
    "Web UI, CLI tools, and full-featured API access"
